posts.post_title: FS: T206 (Letters E-H, plus remaining B-D) (DOUBLE NAME)
posts.post_content:
I'm finally back with more T206s for sale. I've been drastically downsizing my T206 collection, keeping only the top-tier HOFers, Cubs and White Sox, and tough backs. In previous posts I sold cards starting with the letters A, B, C, and D, and now it's time for letters E through H. I've already sold a bunch, and these are the ones that remain from those letters. At the bottom I've also included the eight cards remaining from the letters B, C, and D.

Please PM if interested, or with any questions. PayPal Friends & Family preferred for payment. Add $3 shipping for any number of cards up to $100; free shipping for orders over $100.
